items.title: Why Caterpillar Stock Jumped 11.5% in June
items.description: Any fears about the impact of tariffs on Caterpillar and its stock price appear to be overblown.

items.title: Unifor members at Toromont on strike as they fight for first contract
items.description: Workers at Toromont Industries in Bradford, Ont. went on strike this morning after the employer failed to adequately address wages and benefits during negotiations for a first collective agreement.
